{"tid":2222572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【過火老爺】老爺陪玩摸2歲女心口搣臀部　港媽不安：伸埋手入褲內大髀位","createTime":"2020-09-29T07:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T14:29:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"11fa02191adad1d2d57b7b494993fd17ecb1704b","tid":2222572,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"長輩與小朋友玩得過火，往往令父母感到擔憂，卻又難以開口責備。有港媽近日在網上討論區發文求助，她表示老爺不時會與年幼女兒有過火的身體接觸，不但會伸手入女兒褲內摵大髀，近日更會「揸pat pat」，令港媽覺得尷尬不安。<br />\n<br />\n港媽近日在「親子王國」討論區發文，她表示，女兒快將2歲，每個月都會帶同女兒到老爺奶奶家吃飯1至2次，不過，她發現每次上去，老爺都很喜歡摸女兒，她明白長輩可能單純想跟孩子玩，覺得小朋友很可愛，所以沒有甚麼避忌，但老爺的行為卻令她感到不滿。<br />\n<br />\n老爺伸手入女兒褲內<br />\n她表示，女兒現時走路已很穩定，但老爺仍不時捉住女兒的腋下和心口，不讓女兒自己行，稱擔心女兒跌倒。而在3個月前，有一次到老爺奶奶家，女兒坐在梳化上食餅，老爺又在撩女兒玩。<br />\n&quot;玩玩吓由我個女隻腳掌，搣到伸埋隻手入去褲入面大髀位。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不滿身體接觸過火<br />\n港媽不好意思責怪老爺，只能勸說老爺別再騷擾女兒進食。老爺只在當下停手，但後來又再黏著女兒玩。近日當港媽一家再上去吃飯，老爺開始玩「搣搣」遊戲，甚至叫女兒過去讓他「搣pat pat」，<br />\n&quot;好嘔心！佢係兩隻手都揸晒落去，唔係搣，係揸！我即刻好大聲咁話唔好搣佢pat pat！佢大個喇！女仔嚟！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不過，老爺仍然覺得自己只是在陪玩，維持住哈哈笑聲，不覺自己有問題，反而女兒就被港媽嚇倒。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起網民熱論，不少網民表示，如果港媽介意，應該直接與老爺講清楚，「同奶奶講小朋友唔識嘢，如果被陌生人摸同搣pat pat或者重要部位，以為同佢玩就大鑊」、「你覺得有問題就有責任保護個女！」及「我會直接白啲講，叫佢檢點啲」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2765000/2765321/grandpa_thumb_20200929_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2765000%2F2765321%2Fgrandpa_thumb_20200929_S_1024.jpg&h=841c8e61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3b35b010e3069a5a399eee84cde01e21dfe4da8","tid":2222572,"uid":41411,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"Biden"},{"pid":"16b2a57a7da18697d3df4beca33dd20078939528","tid":2222572,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3b35b010e3069a5a399eee84cde01e21dfe4da8","tid":2222572,"uid":41411,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"Biden"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c724e71a3c24459a88d6e3148275e1a6a55371","tid":2222572,"uid":166062,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"明顯戀童<br />\n<br />\n利伸 戀童"},{"pid":"1498072f2f28174641b086bf0d7c21759906235e","tid":2222572,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d3b35b010e3069a5a399eee84cde01e21dfe4da8","tid":2222572,"uid":41411,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"Biden"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.wakingtimes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Creepy-Joe-Biden.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakingtimes.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FCreepy-Joe-Biden.jpg&h=4674cab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"460567f7cc10688a4b08b28f0b49f25120ff1d9a","tid":2222572,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d23ef9c5c1f13b2a4e8978d2faefa38f0a35c","tid":2222572,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"仲癲撚過China Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe55d3e956f962771ce826e4e63eab8749b16072","tid":2222572,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x0nSn8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0nSn8C.jpg&h=561b63b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f3f1c893880b96c151f83f7f024f9025c3081ed","tid":2222572,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:58:46.000Z","msg":"好心content farm嘅文就唔好響度share啦"},{"pid":"c5de1ab166a5afc9a3bbdb503facb77f0032afd7","tid":2222572,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited